 COPS were on time to stop what could have been another bloody heist. COPS in the Free State province stopped cash van robbery
on Thursday, when they pounced on the armed thugs who were planning to hit the cash van. The cops operation managed to intercept the thugs before they
launched their attack the money truck. The incident occurred 10km before Qwaqwa from Bethlehem. The men were arrested and several guns were also recovered.  